WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Campus Safety at Western Illinois University
[music in background; WIU campus scene]

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Lock Your Door

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.000
[students hanging out in residence hall room]
Emily: I'm hungry. Zach: Me too. Wanna go get food?
Emily: Yeah.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:26.000
[Students exit room to walk to a campus dining center.]

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
[After exiting her room, Emily does not lock the door to her room.]

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.000
[Thief waiting in stairwell waits for Zach and Emily to leave the hallway.]

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.000
[Emily and Zach walk down hall toward exit.]

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:41.000
[Thief from stairwell enters hallway and starts checking doors to see if they're locked.]

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:46.000
[Thief is able to get into Emily's unlocked room and enters.]

00:00:46.000 --> 00:01:05.000
[Thief, now in Emily's room, begins to pick up items—laptops, phone—and place them into his backpack.]

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.000
[Thief hurriedly exits Emily's room after stealing two computers and a mobile phone.]

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.000
[Thief enters hallway and quickly leaves the floor via the stairwell door.]

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:15.000
20 Minutes Later

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
[Zach and Amy in hallway, walking toward Emily's room]
Zach: Man, those cheeseburgers were so good tonight!

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:25.000
[Emily opens door to her unlocked residence hall room. Emily and Zach enter the room.]

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.490
Emily: Oh poop! My laptop is gone!

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:31.500
Zach: Fiddlesticks! My laptop is gone too!

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:34.500
Emily: Ugh! I should have locked the door!

00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:36.000
Thief [in Emily's room]: 
Make sure you always lock your door.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.000
[Emily outside of her room, locking her door. She gives the "thumbs up" signal.]

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.000
Thief: So you're not my next victim.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.000
[Office of Public Safety officers in residence hall]
Officer Van Vlymen: Hi I'm officer Van Vlymen.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:50.210
Detective Worthington: And I'm detective Worthington.
And what you just saw was a dramatization
of what could happen when you don't lock your door.

00:01:50.210 --> 00:01:54.210
Officer Van Vlymen: The easiest way
to prevent this is to always lock your door.

00:01:54.210 --> 00:01:58.000
Detective Worthington: This kind of thing
happens far too often and is really easy to prevent.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:01.000
Officer Van Vlymen: So, please, always
lock your door.

